com.primavera.integration.client.bo.enm

Class GlobalPrivilege

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.primavera.integration.client.bo.enm.EnumType
      • com.primavera.integration.client.bo.enm.GlobalPrivilege

  • public class GlobalPrivilege
extends EnumType
    Global privilege enumerations are used with global profiles to access specific privileges.

    To use an enumeration in a where clause, make sure you use the internal database value. This can be retrieved from a particular enum instance by calling getValue().
